text: James Arnold Taylor (born July 22, 1969) is an American actor and voice actor. He has voiced Obi-Wan Kenobi, Plo Koon and other Star Wars characters. He voices Obi-Wan Kenobi in Star Wars: The Clone Wars and Star Wars: Rebels. He also voices Johnny Test and Fred Flintstone. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:American voice actors Category:Living people
